data.chText: 象牙；（某些其他动物的）长牙
data.enText: a hard yellowish-white substance like bone that forms the tusks (= long teeth) of elephants and some other animals
a ban on the ivory trade

tr: a shade of white the color of bleached bones
a hard smooth ivory colored dentine that makes up most of the tusks of elephants and walruses

value.def: Ivory is a hard cream-coloured substance which forms the tusks of elephants. It is valuable and can be used for making carved ornaments.

example.ex: ...the international ban on the sale of ivory.
example.tran: 禁止销售象牙的国际禁令

trans: 象牙塔(指逃避问题、脱离现实的小天地)
